data.description: Welcome Home. This lovely 5 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home is located in the Clubhouse Community of Grande Park. The two story foyer with hardwood floors lead you into the Formal Living and Dining Room with custom wood trim.  The large open Kitchen has hardwood floors, lots of maple cabinets, a center island, stainless steel appliances and solid surface counters with tile backsplash.  The Breakfast area leads to the ample Family Room with vaulted ceiling, wood burning fireplace and built in surround sound speakers. The 5th Bedroom with walk in closet can be used as an Office. There is also a half bath and large laundry room on the first level. Upstairs you'll find the Owners Suite with double closets, and a luxury bath with double sinks, vanity seating, large step up whirlpool tub, separate shower and private toilet area. There are three additional ample size bedrooms and a second bath. The expansive unfinished basement has rough in plumbing and is ready for your finishing ideas. The 3 car garage with epoxy flooring has plenty of storage for bikes and gardening equipment. The professionally landscaped fenced yard has an inground sprinkler system, landscape lighting and a large brick paver patio as well as a gas connection for an outdoor grill. Additional features: alarm system and smart doorbell.  Enjoy all the amenities Grande Park has to offer: beautiful Clubhouse, Pools, Miles of Walking Trails, Ponds, Tennis Courts, Sledding Hill, Sports Fields, Parks, Playgrounds and Ponds.  District 308 Elementary and Middle Schools located within walking distance.  Close to Downtown Plainfield with lots of dining options as well as Rt 59 shopping corridor.
